Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Fix typo adding CPPFLAGS to XCC

---
 configure | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/configure b/configure
index c54028a..d173838 100755
--- a/configure
